"quote":{"pid":"ffcad6b049c11223716f545a3da61b379a0177b9","tid":1873301,"uid":254183,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T14:41:46.000Z","msg":"支那的經濟命脈都係工業<br />\n冇可能像香港home office"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T14:50:25.000Z","msg":"商業呢？"},{"pid":"6cd477df068c4f78523bdb71be01f4a9970e7b84","tid":1873301,"uid":198175,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T14:54:23.000Z","msg":"冇罩用, 冇車坐, 門口都出唔到, 點開工?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a785d425ce3bbc7e8fb27d8aebef3c8a7dd2e14","tid":1873301,"uid":181088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T14:54:37.000Z","msg":"廣東細廠<br />\n公司今日掛名開工<br />\n得office開工<br />\n工廠員工要每日睇溫度<br />\n4日都正常先可以開工<br />\n（姐係工場最快要星期五先開）<br />\n但村委會好似唔撚想比我地開咁死都唔出批文<br />\n<br />\n另外原材料商都冇一間開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3abbc392a60a5841cda731add574228d11605e91","tid":1873301,"uid":64962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T14:55:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e83b51d54585ebc6e5e578ae5a7620af73c200","tid":1873301,"uid":331421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T15:00:04.000Z","msg":"復工實唔夠口罩用"},{"pid":"699207b3681c43da7c547ca6166123bc1be0872b","tid":1873301,"uid":33916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T15:00:19.000Z","msg":"有正苦permit 有工開<br />\n但係員工要隔離幾多日先可以開工視乎local 正苦要求<br />\n但係更多人冇口罩出唔倒發番工廠番工<br />\n開黎都唔知做乜鳩<br />\n<br />\n深圳廠隔離街爆緊case都可以批開工<br />\n武漢竟然吹緊下星期開工 (我就唔撚信)<br />\n北邊海邊大城唔俾開<br />\n<br />\n利: 公司係支那有幾間廠"},{"pid":"e27067a90df1e047663bbd10e58c45ae2c8c4653","tid":1873301,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T15:45:03.000Z","msg":"上海堆金融office 呢？"},{"pid":"7e0dbf32ddf84d265832a6586f146d7a59fb5d07","tid":1873301,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi